    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" resp="#JP">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>Θάλπων χαῖρε
                    <lb n="2" />χρηστὲ καὶ ἄμε<hi rend="small">μ</hi>
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>πτε <g type="interpunct">·</g> Θάλπ<unclear>ο</unclear>ν
                    <lb n="4"/>ἐνθάδε κεῖμαι ἑξα
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>ετὴς δὲ θανών
                    <lb n="6"/>νήπιος ὠκύμορος
               </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp><app><note>Text from autopsy</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Thalpon, farewell, worthy and blameless Thalpon! Here I lie, having died aged six, a child of swift fate.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#Ferrua">
                <p>Talpone, addio, buono ed irreprensibile Talpone! Qui giaccio, e morto a sei anni, bambine di celere fato.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The name Thalpon is not otherwise attested.</p>
            </div>
